import React from 'react' import { VscDebugRestart } from 'react-icons/vsc' import { AiFillQuestionCircle } from 'react-icons/ai' import micromodal from 'micromodal' const CompletedPage = (props) => { const createWrongQuestions = () => { let answerString = '' for (let i = 0; i < props.wrongQuestions.length; i++) { if (i == props.wrongQuestions.length - 1) { answerString += props.wrongQuestions[i] } else { answerString += props.wrongQuestions[i] + ', ' } } return answerString } return (

You've Completed the Test!

You Guessed {props.points} Questions
of the 30 Correctly!

{ props.setPoints(0) }} href='/'>

Mykael.Barnes@hotmail.com

) } export default CompletedPage
